"Markz" is a Chrome plugin that allows users to leave comments on any web page in real-time. With this extension, you can:
- Interact with subscribers directly on the page;
- Discuss topics of interest without switching to third-party platforms;
- Receive notifications about new comments and reviews related to sections or sites of interest to you;
- Enrich your online experience, making it more interactive and socially oriented.
